Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 大家在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家…在哪兒…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴 貴月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搭著這艘飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來到了這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 不是這個星球的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對 我得知了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不作驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挺SF的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.23,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}SF：Science Fiction的縮寫 科幻的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個 動不了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為在來這個星球的途中遭遇了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以現在處於無法航行的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}系統也出了些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來是打算住在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才搬到了霧島同學的家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然也有…別的一些緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 剛才那個有稜有角的機器是啥來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是來襲擊你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在緊急情況使用的救援飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被這艘船它…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自動發出的救難信號給叫來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}救助我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把那個破壞了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…順其自然就
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順其自然？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這艘飛船動不了是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣沒得到救援 好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好是不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我還想留在這個星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是來尋找…這個星球上的某個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}某個地方而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}某個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我記憶中的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然也不知道是不是真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是想找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐是外星人這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說就算說了學姐是外星人也沒人信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過要是被黑衣人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(682,662)}Men in black
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒這種組織啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被…被解剖什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來學姐在擔心這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因…因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐 我也不會對任何人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 不會對任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你們添麻煩了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能參觀參觀這兒不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 這時候你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是 這種機會可不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻也這麼想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實挺有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 這個果然很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}超方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽他們肯定在擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒辦法 我送你回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 把老姐給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 留你們那麼晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓你們聽我說我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別擔心 一夏你一如往常就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真嚇了一跳呢 貴月學姐是外星人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說我現在都無法相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和我說這是在整人還可信點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 我是之前就稍稍有些感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然好像是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻感覺不能完全否定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的哦 因為我是黑衣人的特工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說這玩笑算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐那麼怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺…發生了各種事 真是了不得的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}趕緊回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…還有事情沒對海人說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搭著太空船 第一次到這個星球的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…讓海人你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候學姐如果沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可能 就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與其說是知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如說是我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我用了我星球的技術進行了治療
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我怕還有什麼問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以來到我家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只是意外還是啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就此也讓我能遇上學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 真的挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對 成問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不是學姐是外星人這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事啦 不用道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家講了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反而感覺更輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過 如果聯盟安保局得知救援飛船被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能會派出調查員的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}若是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能會給大家添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又…會傷害大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}時間非常有限
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的時間只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻好久都沒來過我家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 突然就說要來過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這倒是沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想 柑菜大概在迷惘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那也是啊 畢竟知道了貴月學姐是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是說關於霧島同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學 他有何打算呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐是外星人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說她終有一日會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要一想到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺自己就變成很討人厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變成了很狡猾的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}狡猾也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「喜歡」是停不下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}停不下來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說你為啥知道我的心意啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有目共睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至今為止真的承蒙你的關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你的事 以及在這裡度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我絕對 絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論是打工還是什麼我都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對會去與你相會的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我的老家在仙女座哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(770,662)}Andromeda
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離這裡兩百三十萬光年啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}宇宙 可真廣闊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我稍微出一下門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 出門是去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說 是要去「那個地方」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早飯我已經做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午飯之前我會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}繼續待在這個星球的話 會給大家添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明現在就馬上呼叫救援來得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼我會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然還是別這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為 才隔了一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準確來說還不到一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不知道該怎麼和貴月學姐交往好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用想太多 像往常一樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼能不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻 你剪了頭髮之後好像連性格都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都…沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你們倆在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛 貴月學姐出門去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是要去找昨天說的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然一個人去了 也太見外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要說一聲 我們肯定會鼎力相助的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她應該有很多自己的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來拍攝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好 再往裡面一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再被打得慘一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是以同班同學的傳言為契機的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}轉學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}據說是公所那個霧島爺爺的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 那個孤僻的老頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽我媽說是因為父母因事故身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以就回到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家 都回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來介紹一位從今天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就將和大家一同學習的轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是從東京來的 名叫霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼說著 面帶微笑的他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實在看不出來是剛剛失去父母的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}設身處地的想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那絕對不是能笑得出來的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便如此還能面帶笑容的他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想我大概…從那時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就開始在意他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他那時候的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和現在的海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重疊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第九話 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}膠捲不夠的話再買就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有就是…姑且把傘什麼的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也要去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請讓我也幫一下忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影的拍攝我也拜託了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暫時休息一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從現在開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一個人去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能再給海人添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再說這也是我個人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是說了今天不用拍攝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來了會礙事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒是不礙事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是說西瓜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐 又出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼沒有去幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說什麼是個人問題然後被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還叫我加油拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想起了一個還沒拍的風景鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去一下輕井澤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你要回去的話拜託關好門窗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鑰匙放在老地方就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說什麼「就好」 那這個該怎麼處理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼搞的 又是西瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是要去拍風景鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個 是在輕井澤時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍得好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 貴月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 還拍了這種場景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來吃西瓜吧 西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真可愛的正太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要和我約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請容我敬謝不敏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在焦躁不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看起來是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理由嘛 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如說和一夏之間發生了什麼之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都沒發生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 她什麼都不讓我發生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐不會懂我的感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是孩子氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為事與願違就鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 你可又懂得一夏的感受呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你覺得一夏是有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因何想法獨身來到這個星球的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在又是有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因何想法而行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學你有想過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對於鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}表明自己真實身份的一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有作出何種回應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是在叫你去想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你能為一夏做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果你心中有一夏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想必已經有答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要「停滯」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海那傢伙 在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最近老不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電話也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小智你個笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不回去了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你差不多該回去了吧 老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經調查過FD32了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來是PF…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪兒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又要去找那個「地方」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果找到了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺你好像會道一聲「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後就回到你的星球去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反而是件幸運的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡海人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果少了個對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那還真是讓我偷笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也發覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐心裡也一定明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還…發現了另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐也…喜歡海人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你會說因為是外星人所以不行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還會說因為不能一直待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以無法回應海人的心意是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就打算用著這樣的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直從海人身邊逃開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說逃什麼的…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但你現在卻就在這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在找那個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}假裝拼命的去找那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實是想把視線從海人身上移開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是我能有什麼辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我又不能一直在這個星…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把「喜歡」說出來就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和喜歡的人在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管我如何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都無法得到的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對你而言卻是那麼的唾手可得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總是找藉口牽強附會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總是這麼逃避著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明連海人他…正在做什麼都不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種事情自己去問！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…你會在這裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看著我被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那麼有意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}假裝是要支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就為了看我這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}低級趣味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你走啊 回去啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓我哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡海人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有樹有池塘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡會有些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做著這種漂亮事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為我找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得我是不得不回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給大家添了這麼多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學她…讓我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不想回去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並只是想去那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是外星人也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我這樣的人也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向你表白也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}定是…從我們初遇起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:17.47,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡上了…你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:29.84,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…那啥…我是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.82,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.67,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是第四次了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.16,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第一次是在水壩那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.16,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第二次是你倒在玄關的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:43.92,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第三次是被救援飛船襲擊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.27,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全部是和我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:48.67,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了把我身體中的奈米醫療機器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.36,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}輸送給海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.01,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能吻合真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:54.55,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:22:57.76,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一點兒也不浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.06,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:00.63,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:03.92,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是第五次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}龐若是有了悲傷才有快樂那般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在某人幸福的背後卻有人流下了淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻停不下 我強烈的思念

